videos.headline: Cook roasts Hogs to produce Missouri victory party
videos.description: Mizzou becomes bowl eligible as QB Brady Cook accounts for 380 total yards (242 passing, 138 rushing) and two TDs in a 29-27 win over visiting Arkansas.
